data.description: Modern 3-Bedroom Home with Pool and Corner Lot! Stylish and comfortable home. Newly renewed and modern 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is situated on a spacious corner lot.  Features:3 bedrooms, perfect for families or individuals needing extra space, 2 bathrooms, ensuring comfort and privacy for everyone. Inviting pool, ideal for relaxation and outdoor entertainment. Generous corner lot, providing ample outdoor space for gardening or play. Modern interior design, with sleek finishes and updated fixtures. Recently renewed, ensuring a fresh and up-to-date living experience.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exquisite property your new home.
